criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Being 60 years old or older;

          -  Retired;

          -  Accept the invitation to participate in the singing group program;

          -  Not having participated in other intervention programs in the previous four months.

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Having a severe impairment, that is disabling for the participation in the singing
             group activity (e.g. severe cognitive, auditory, visual or mobility impairments).
